videos.description: Zach Edey scores back-to-back buckets in the second half, highlighting his big half and a 17-0 run for Purdue.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Edey’s back-to-back buckets highlight Purdue’s 17-0 run) 2022/01/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Edey's back-to-back buckets highlight Purdue's 17-0 run

videos.description: Sasha Stefanovic cans the long 3-pointer and has some words for the crowd.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Purdue’s Stefanovic quiets the crowd with a deep triple) 2022/01/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Purdue's Stefanovic quiets the crowd with a deep triple

videos.description: Illinois guard Da'Monte Williams denies Jaden Ivey with the impressive transition block.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Illinois’ Williams skies for the huge block) 2022/01/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Illinois' Williams skies for the huge block

videos.description: Jaden Ivey emphatically swats Alfonso Plummer's shout out of bounds for the huge block.

videos.headline: Purdue's Ivey spikes a block out of bounds

videos.description: Andre Curbelo goes baseline for the layup, bringing Illinois even late in the second half.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Curbelo ties it for Illinois with clutch layup) 2022/01/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Curbelo ties it for Illinois with clutch layup

videos.description: Andre Curbelo loses the ball, gets it back, and still is able to find Alfonso Plummer for the layup, tying the score and sending it to double overtime.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Broken play ends up with Illinois bucket, sending game to double OT) 2022/01/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Broken play ends up with Illinois bucket, sending game to double OT

videos.description: Illinois gets key buckets to send the game to overtime and double overtime, but Purdue's Trevion Williams makes a couple clutch plays late for the win.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Purdue hangs on for wild double OT win over Illinois) 2022/01/17 ESHEET
